#

Tomato and Mozzarella Toast

15 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Snack

Tags:

QuickHealthyLight Meal

Description

A delightful, fresh, and easy-to-make open-faced sandwich combining ripe tomatoes and creamy mozzarella on crisped bread, perfect for a light meal or snack.

Ingredients

  • sourdough bread: 2 slices
  • ripe tomatoes: 1 large, sliced
  • fresh mozzarella cheese: 100 grams, sliced
  • fresh basil leaves: a handful
  • balsamic glaze: to drizzle
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
